      "content": "I hear you, and I'm feeling the same way. But it’s not really up to me to negotiate with them—the email said the update is being rolled out automatically across all their partner accounts. They basically said it's non-negotiable to ensure the \"brand identity\" is uniform. I'm supposed to initiate the update process during our next sync to make sure the new constraints are applied to my workspace. What do you think we should do?",
